         <abstract>
            <p>A type of ʾƎgziʾabǝḥer nagśa collection which developed from  <ref type="work" corresp="LIT1326egziab"/>.
               Its <foreign xml:lang="gez">ʿĀrke</foreign>-hymns seem to have been included in the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2375Synaxa"/>.
               <persName ref="PRS6378Ludolf"/> used it to compile his calendar in 
            <bibl>
                  <ptr target="bm:Ludolf1691Commentarius"/>
                  <citedRange unit="page">389-427</citedRange>
               </bibl>.</p>
